data.description: This stunning 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home with bonus room has so much to offer. Step inside to discover an inviting interior flooded with natural light, the spacious living area is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying cozy evenings with loved ones. The adjacent kitchen features modern appliances, ample cabinet space, with an extra large pantry closet. Retreat to the comfortable master suite, complete with a private en-suite bathroom for ultimate relaxation and privacy. Two additional bedrooms offer versatility for a growing family, home office, or guest accommodations. The spacious basement features two large living areas ideal for entertainment or relaxation. The bonus room with walk-in closets offers additional space for a home office, gym, or guests. There is also two large storage spaces. Outside, you'll find over an acre of land, with a beautifully landscaped yard, ideal for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying the serene surroundings and a patio area ready for a evening around the fire pit. Don't miss your chance to own this delightful home in one of Elizabethtown's most desirable neighborhoods. Schedule your showing today!
